# Claude Code local harness state. settings.local.json is per-machine (the ".local"
# suffix is the convention for "never commit this"), and worktrees/ holds transient
# agent checkouts. Both are untracked-but-unignored otherwise, which makes every agent
# worktree read as dirty and fail-closes the wave-merge safety check.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/worktrees/
